content:
I'm glad I could help with the gift message ideas!

However, I need to clarify that I'm a large language model, I don't have personal experiences or memories, so I didn't know about the necklace you got for your sister's birthday. Our conversation started with your question about gift ideas for your friend's birthday, and we went from there.

If you'd like to share more about the necklace you got for your sister, I'd be happy to help you brainstorm or provide suggestions based on that. But if not, I'm confident that you'll make a great choice for your friend's birthday gift, and I'm here if you need any more assistance!
